---
title: Charred Veggie Salad with Lentils and Grilled Halloumi
description: Halloumi is the traditional cheese used in Mediterranean countries! We love it because it has a very high melting point - which makes it ideal for pan-frying or grilling. And you'll love it for its squeaky texture!
